# --- project workspaces (compositions/artifacts) -- git-ignored except the committed template ---
projects/*
!projects/_example/

# --- shared CAD model binaries: regenerable/refetchable cache, NOT committed (decision 2026-06-24) ---
# (the catalog DEFS in library*/ ARE committed; only the heavy 3D model binaries are ignored.
#  generated parts regenerate; catalog-fetched parts refetch via data/. drawings .pdf/.png/.dwg kept.)
cad/*.glb
cad/*.step
cad/*.stp
cad/*.zip

# --- legacy root artifacts (migrate into projects/<name>/out/, then delete) ---
out/
out_*.txt
*.output
jl.json

# NOTE: files already staged/tracked are NOT auto-ignored -- run `git rm -r --cached <path>`
# (e.g. cad/*.glb cad/*.step out/) during migration A to actually stop tracking them.
